<title>HUNGARY: BORSODCHEM H1 '97 AFTER-TAX PROFIT.</title>
<headline>BORSODCHEM H1 '97 AFTER-TAX PROFIT.</headline>
<dateline>BUDAPEST 1997-07-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six-month period ending June</p>
<p>30.</p>
<p>(Figures in millions of forints unless stated)</p>
<p>					  Jan-June 1997   Jan-June 1996</p>
<p>    Group operating profit	   4,010.7   vs   3,539.3</p>
<p>    Group pre-tax profit	     4,401.1   vs   4,101.1</p>
<p>    Group after-tax profit	   3,621.2   vs   3,361.5</p>
<p>    Group net sales		   29,596.2   vs  21,332.6</p>
<p>    Group other revenue		  981.1   vs     680.1</p>
<p>    Group direct costs of sales   22,080.4   vs  13,463.4</p>
<p>    Group indirect costs of sales  3,541.1   vs   4,045.7</p>
<p>    Group other expenditures	   945.1   vs     964.3</p>
<p>    Group net financial income     390.3 profit vs 560.0 profit</p>
<p>    Group net extraordinary income   0.2 profit vs   1.8 profit</p>
<p>    Taxation				 786.4   vs     747.3</p>
<p>NOTE - BorsodChem Rt is a chemicals company.</p>
<p>The figures are consolidated, were calculated in accordance</p>
<p>with Hungarian Accounting Standards and are not audited.</p>
<p>-- Budapest newsroom +36 1 327-4040</p>
